com.symantec.dlpx.flexresponse.configuration

Interface ConfigurationParameter<T>


  • public interface ConfigurationParameter<T>
    A parameter that provides configuration information to a FlexResponse plugin. Configuration values from the plugin properties file are one source of configuration parameters. Configurarion parameters can be of 2 types: either String or StoredCredential. A plugin author should preferably use the methods ConfigurationParameters.getStringValue(String) and ConfigurationParameters.getCredentialValue(String).
